ull, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016410, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This prayer has been tested regarding the accomplishment of important demands, and if a person’s demand is not fulfilled in the 1st week, he should offer it again in the 2nd week, and if it is not fulfilled in the second week as well, he should again offer this prayer in the 3rd week as it will be certainly fulfilled thereupon. Syed Mohammad Ali Jawaheri Haeri said to me: I offered this prayer for the fulfillment of a demand and in the same night, I witnessed Imam Mahdi (a) in the state of dream, I expressed my demand before him and Allah (swt) accomplished it due to the grace of his holiness (a). He has also said that: I have experienced this prayer for myself as well.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh amal har ahem haajat ke liye mujjarab (akseer) hai agar in do (2) raato’n mein haajat poori na ho dobaara (phir se) dusre hafte (2nd week) mein is amal ko anjaam de, agar phir bhi haajat qabool na huwi to phir se thisre hafte (3rd week) mein anjaam de yaqeenan uski haajat qabool hogi. Saaheb-e-Kitaab Al-Tohfatur Razviya ne kaha hai keh Syed Muhammad Ali Jawaaheri ne mujh se naql kiya hai keh jo is namaz ko haajat ke liye anjaam deta hai usi raat Hazrat Imam Mahdi (a) ko khwaab mein dekhta hai aur apni haajat ko Hazrat ki khidmat mein pesh karta hai. Khuda wanda taala Imam-e-Zamana (a) ki barkat se uski mushkil ko hal aur uski haajat ko poori karta hai.", "UrduDescription": "یہ عمل ہر مہم حاجت کے لئے مجّرب ہے اگر ان دو راتوں میں حاجت پوری نہ ہو دوبارہ دوسرے ہفتہ میں اس عمل کو انجام دے اگر پھر بھی حاجت قبول نہ ہوئی دوبارہ تیسرے ہفتہ میں انجام دے یقینا اس کی حاجت قبول ہوگی صاحب کتاب التحفة الرضویہ نے کہا ہے کہ سید محمد علی جواہری حائری نے مجھ سے نقل کیا ہے کہ جو اس نماز کو حاجت کے لئے انجام دیتاہے اسی رات حضرت امام مھدی کو خواب میں دیکھتاہے اور اپنی حاجت کو حضرت کی خدمت میں پیش کرتاہے خداوند تعالیٰ امام زمانہ کی برکت سے اس کی مشکل کو حل اور اس کی حاجت کو پوری کرتاہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, 